text.section:
The fiscal court shall provide for the incarceration of prisoners by:
Providing and maintaining a facility that complies with KRS 441.055;
Providing and maintaining a safe, secure, and clean jail in the county; or that complies with the health and life safety standards defined in KRS 441.055;
Contracting with another county or a city for the incarceration and care of its prisoners; and
Providing for the transportation of prisoners, as provided for in KRS 441.505 and 441.510 including the provision of vehicles, drivers, and guards.
